“And I know that Sikorsky and the state of Connecticut are very proud to contribute to our national security, and I assume that hundreds, if not even thousands of people depend on it.
And I think like most Americans, we are all proud of the helicopters and other military equipment for which so many Americans have worked tirelessly.
Of course, it is appropriate to emphasize this.”
